Especially in India, these latest iPhone 15 variants may cost you a hefty amount. Don’t worry! You can buy your latest iPhone without breaking your bank account.

    How?

    Read on to learn.

    Here is the solution to it – Go the extra mile!

So, without further ado, let us get started. Apple has launched its iPhone 15 series with many storage options. Let’s check them out with one by one.

    Should You Buy the iPhone 15 in 2025? Comparing with iPhone 16 and Market Trends

    The Apple iPhone 15 series arrived back in September 2023. Since then, Apple has released the iPhone 16 and iPhone 16 Pro series in September 2024. Which means new features and performance improvements have been added in the journey. Since, iPhone 15 series has been there for a while now (a year older), prices have adjusted in many markets. Discounts have been commonly available for this particular model. Here’s how the iPhone 15 series stacks up in 2025, along with key considerations for buyers looking to save money or get the latest technology.

    Updated Pricing and Discounts in 2025

    As of June 2025, iPhone 15 models are often available at reduced prices due to the release of the iPhone 16 series. For example:

    • India: The iPhone 15 (128GB) is now available for as low as Rs. 69,900 to 74,900 during promotions (e.g., Amazon India or Flipkart sales with bank offers).
    • US: Prices have dropped to ~$699 to 749 for the iPhone 15 (128GB), equivalent to ~Rs. 58,000 to 62,000 at current exchange rates (excluding taxes).
    • Dubai: Tax-free prices are around AED 2,799 to 3,099 (~Rs. 63,000–70,000) for the iPhone 15 (128GB).
    • Check local retailers or Apple’s refurbished store for certified pre-owned units at even lower prices, often 10–15 per cent cheaper than new models.

    Always verify current prices, as exchange rates and seasonal discounts (e.g., Black Friday, festive sales) can significantly lower costs.

    Also read: Apple iPhones Eligible For iOS 26: Check Supported Devices

    Where To Buy Your iPhone 15 As Price Varies in Different Countries?

    Hope this extensive analysis will help you understand the remarkable iPhone 15 price differences in various countries. You can buy the iPhone 15 from the USA and Dubai at the cheapest price. However, the Indian market will cost you much more than other markets.

    So, if you are planning to purchase the iPhone 15, verify the prices from this article on how the iPhone 15 price varies in different countries. This comparison article can be a valuable resource for you.
